  <title>Software Applications and Environments</title>

  <p>RCS installs and maintains software applications and environments on the HBS Grid. A wide base of system
  libraries like <app>ImageMagick</app> and <app>Tesseract</app> are available, allowing you to do
  <em>image processing</em> and <em>optical character recognition</em> in <app>R</app> (among many other things).
  A wide selection of graphical desktop applications for math, statistics, data analysis, data management,
  communication, manuscript preparation, and system configuration are also available.</p>

